Description . Size: Holotype : body length (to elytral apices) 2.2 mm ; max. width (elytra) 0.77 mm . Head, pronotum and elytra black to blackish brown, somewhat lighter at all margins. Venter, lateral hypomera and pseudepipleura paler, with darker mentum. Legs reddish-brown; tarsi and maxilliary palps paler, especially towards their apices (
Fig. 1
).
